adidas Forum Wings 4.0 Jeremy Scott Blue Gradient
results.story: The Jeremy Scott x adidas Forum Wings 4.0 ‘Gradient’ complements the shoe’s outlandish details with a vibrant color palette. Embellished with a pair of molded wings that wrap around the collar, the high-top sports a leather upper in a bold shade of royal blue that ultimately transitions to a pastel lime green hue. Pink serrated three-stripes adorn the quarter panel, while a jeweled adidas logo graces the adjustable ankle strap. The sneaker is mounted on a solid black rubber cupsole with an exposed EVA wedge on the medial side.

results.name: adidas Y-3 Qisan Cozy Black Chalk White
results.story: The adidas Y-3 Qisan Cozy 'Black Chalk Pearl' introduces a new silhouette that blends progressive style with modern performance technology. The slip-on upper is crafted from stretchy black neoprene with tonal synthetic overlays and dual webbing pull tabs for easy on and off. White three-stripes decorate the quarter panel, while Y-3 branding is embossed on the molded heel patch. The sneaker is mounted on an exaggerated Lightstrike midsole, featuring an exposed TPU shank plate for torsional support.

adidas Harden Vol. 6 Gren Mist Pulse Aqua
results.story: The adidas Harden Vol. 6 ‘Green Mist Pulse Aqua’ updates James Harden’s signature shoe with responsive cushioning and a sustainable build. A pale green hue permeates a textile and synthetic upper made in part with recycled materials, generated from a blend of production scraps and post-consumer waste. A breathable mesh tongue and interior foam pods combine for a comfortable fit. The low-top rides on a full-length Boost midsole, reinforced with an aqua-colored cage on the lateral sidewall for improved stability. Underfoot, a herringbone-tread rubber outsole offers stop-and-go traction.

results.name: adidas Harden Vol. 6 Pulse Aqua Solar Yellow
results.colorway: Pulse Aqua/Team Semi Sol Orange/Solar Yellow
results.story: The adidas Harden Vol. 6 'Pulse Aqua Solar Yellow' delivers a vivid installment in James Harden’s signature series. Made in part with recycled content, an aqua-colored textile upper features tonal no-sew skins and a trio of orange webbing pull tabs for easy on and off. A breathable mesh tongue combines with foam pods throughout the interior heel for a comfortable fit. Responsive cushioning is provided by a full-length Boost midsole, caged on the lateral side and reinforced by a herringbone-traction rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA Lunar New Year (2022)
adidas Swim Slide Beyonce Ivy Park Ivy Heart
results.story: Launching as part of a collaborative collection with the athleisure label co-founded by Beyoncé, the Ivy Park x adidas Slide ‘Ivy Heart’ pairs a monochrome finish with a premium build. The wide bandage-strap upper is crafted from tumbled leather and lined in soft textile for a comfortable fit. Stamped in gold lettering, dual adidas and Ivy Park branding decorates the raised and contoured footbed. An exaggerated foam midsole offers lightweight cushioning with each step.

adidas Savage Beyonce Ivy Park Halls of Ivy
results.story: Dropping as part of the fifth collection with Beyoncé’s athleisure brand, the Ivy Park x adidas Savage V4 ‘Halls of Ivy’ brings back an archival trail shoe from 1999. The upper is crafted from white textile with wavy overlays in contrasting tan and black hues. Webbing three-stripes in Wild Pine adorn the quarter panel, while Ivy Park branding is embroidered on the heel overlay. The sneaker rides on a sculpted green foam midsole, supported underfoot by a lugged Traxion rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Super Sleek Chunky Beyonce Ivy Park Halls of Ivy (W)
results.story: The Ivy Park x adidas Super Sleek Chunky ‘Halls of Ivy’ is taken from the fifth collaborative collection with the athleisure brand co-founded by Beyoncé. This fashion-forward take on the adidas Samba features an off-white corduroy upper with tonal leather three-stripes and grey premium suede overlays. Details include mismatched Ivy Park and adidas tongue tags, a navy leather-lined interior, and coiled bungee detailing at the heel. The low-profile design up top is offset by a chunky platform sole unit with segmented sidewalls.

results.name: adidas Super Sleek Boot Beyonce Ivy Park Halls of Ivy
results.story: Launching as part of the fifth collection with Beyoncé’s athleisure brand, the Ivy Park x adidas Super Sleek Boot ‘Halls of Ivy’ presents a sneaker-boot hybrid that draws inspiration from the classic Samba. A monochromatic olive green finish is applied to the upper, lined in warm Sherpa fleece and built with a blend of ballistic mesh and premium suede. Utilitarian details include D-ring eyelets and a coiled bungee strap that wraps around the high-cut collar. The towering silhouette is anchored by a gum rubber platform sole.

results.name: adidas Adizero Adios Pro 2 Legacy Indigo Turbo
results.story: The adidas Adizero Adios Pro 2 ‘Legacy Indigo Turbo’ showcases vibrant hues on a performance running shoe designed with direct input from world-class athletes. Made with 50% recycled content, the semi-translucent textile upper is rendered in a gradient blue finish with oversized three-stripes in a bright red hue. The cushioned midsole is composed of two layers of Lightstrike Pro foam, enhanced with a series of carbon-infused EnergyRods for limited energy loss. The outsole features grippy Continental Rubber under the forefoot and heel.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost OG Beyonce Ivy Park Solar Green
results.story: Launching as part of the fifth collaborative collection with the athleisure brand co-founded by Beyoncé, the Ivy Park x adidas UltraBoost OG ‘Halls of Ivy’ treats the running shoe to a monochrome neon green makeover. Drawcord lacing secures the flexible Primeknit upper, bolstered with a molded midfoot cage and external heel counter. Dual adidas and Ivy Park branding decorates the sockliner. The sneaker sits atop a full-length Boost midsole, reinforced underfoot by a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Y-3 Qisan Cozy Black Bliss Red
results.story: The adidas Y-3 Qisan Cozy ‘Bliss Black’ debuts a lifestyle runner that blends adidas performance technology with styling inspired by the Y-3 Qasa. The slip-on features a stretchy neoprene upper with contrasting black, off-white and crimson paneling. Suede and rubberized overlays bolster the lightweight build, while dual webbing pull tabs provide easy on and off. The sneaker sits atop a stacked Lightstrike midsole, featuring a red TPU plate sandwiched between the two layers.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost OG Beyonce Ivy Park Peloton Focus Olive
results.story: The Ivy Park x Peloton x adidas UltraBoost OG ‘Focus Olive’ delivers a three-way collaboration that brings together the Three Stripes with Beyoncé’s athleisure brand and the popular exercise equipment manufacturer. The lightweight running shoe carries an olive green knit upper secured with toggle lace closure. ‘Ivy Park’ is debossed on the tonal heel counter, while the leather tongue tag displays dual adidas and Peloton branding. The sneaker rides atop a matching green Boost midsole, supported underfoot by a neon green Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Adizero Adios Pro 2 Halo Ivory Pink Solar Gold
results.story: The adidas Adizero Adios Pro 2 ‘Halo Ivory Ultra Pop’ enlivens the pinnacle running shoe with color-popped accents. Semi-translucent textile is utilized on the upper, marked with floating pink three-stripes on the lateral side and a ‘NYC 2021’ graphic on the opposing side. An internal fit system provides a feeling of lockdown while reducing pressure on the top of the foot. The midsole, featuring energy-returning Boost with Lightstrike cushioning, works in tandem with a full-length carbon fiber plate. A Continental Rubber outsole yields grippy traction.

adidas Ultra Boost 20 James Bond 007 No Time Do Die Black
results.story: Drawn from a capsule collection inspired by the James Bond film ‘No Time to Die,’ the adidas UltraBoost 20 ‘Triple Black’ showcases a sleek monochromatic finish in a nod to the secret agent’s signature tuxedo. The black Primeknit upper is accented with unique branding elements, including ‘007’ inscribed on the heel and a familiar tongue-tag graphic that references the opening title sequence of every Bond film. Inside the tonal midfoot cage, a hidden pocket provides storage space for tiny spy gadgets. The lightweight runner rides on a matching black Boost midsole, underpinned by a grippy Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA James Bond 007 No Time Do Die Off White
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost DNA ‘Triple White’ is taken from a capsule collection celebrating the release of the James Bond film ‘No Time to Die.’ This pair pays tribute to 007’s sartorial sensibilities, featuring a monochromatic palette inspired by Bond’s tuxedo. Off-white Primeknit is executed on the upper, accented with ‘007’ debossed on the heel and a tongue-tag graphic that nods to the iconic title sequence of all 25 Bond films. The sneaker is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole, supported by a Cloud White Continental rubber outsole and a black tie-inspired Torsion bar.

adidas Adiozero Prime X Sonic Ink Green
results.story: The adidas Adizero Prime X ‘Sonic Ink Screaming Green’ features color-popped accents on a performance running shoe built for long distances. The semi-translucent upper is crafted from Celermesh 2.0, rendered in white and violet with a bright green Slinglaunch Heel for an anti-slip lockdown fit. Three layers of Lightstrike Pro foam are packed into the midsole, enhanced with five carbon-infused EnergyRods designed to spring back with each step. A Continental rubber outsole provides superior grip.

adidas Forum Mid Ivy Park Rodeo Halo Silver
results.story: Launching as part of a comprehensive collection with Beyoncé’s athleisure brand, the Ivy Park x adidas Forum Mid ‘Rodeo’ treats the retro hoops shoe to a neutral one-note finish. Toggle laces secure a grey canvas upper with raw edges and serrated suede three-stripes. Ivy Park branding is found on a rubberized insert on the adjustable strap, as well as a suede tongue tag marked with embroidered lettering in a subtle purple hue. The mid-top rides on a tonal rubber midsole, enhanced with EVA cushioning and reinforced by a semi-translucent rubber outsole.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost OG Beyonce Ivy Park Navy
results.story: Similar to past UltraBoost collaborations with Beyoncé’s athleisure brand, the Ivy Park x adidas UltraBoost OG ‘Night Marine’ pairs refreshed details with a monochromatic palette. Varying shades of blue are applied to the sock-like Primeknit upper, secured with a toggle lacing system and fortified with a TPU midfoot cage. Atop the suede-covered heel counter, traditional UltraBoost branding is replaced by a debossed Ivy Park logo. The sneaker rides on a matching navy Boost midsole, supported underfoot by a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole.

adidas Slides Ivy Park Screaming Orange
results.story: Designed in partnership with Beyoncé’s athleisure imprint, the Ivy Park x adidas Slide ‘Screaming Orange’ applies a vibrant monochromatic finish to a fashionable slip-on sandal made for poolside and beyond. Plush terry cloth is utilized on the wide bandage strap upper, marked with Ivy Park branding in oversized block letters. Step-in comfort is provided by a molded foam footbed, which sits atop an exaggerated rubber sole unit for a lifted look.

adidas Adizero Adios Pro 2 Sonic Ink Screaming Green
results.story: The adidas Adizero Adios Pro 2 ‘Sonic Ink Screaming Green’ adds fluorescent three-stripes to a performance runner designed with input from some of the world’s fastest athletes. Partially made with recycled polyester, the one-piece Celermesh 2.0 upper offers a blend of breathability and support. The lightweight build is mounted on a double-stacked Lightstrike Pro midsole with five carbon-infused EnergyRods for optimized running economy with limited energy loss. Underfoot, a Continental rubber outsole yields grippy traction.

adidas Lette Slide Stella McCartney Core Black (W)
results.story: The Stella McCartney x adidas women’s Lette Slide ‘Core Black’ delivers the British fashion designer’s take on the post-workout sandal. Dual black straps — one in stretchy textile, the other in open mesh —deliver a supportive and comfortable fit. The contoured footbed and glossy EVA midsole are both stamped with adidas and Stella McCartney branding. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a modified herringbone traction pattern for superior grip.

results.name: adidas Ozweego Vapour Steel
results.story: The adidas Ozweego ‘Vapour Steel’ delivers a monochrome edition of the lifestyle runner inspired by the Ozweego 3 from 1998. Like its namesake, the sneaker features a uniquely shaped eyestay and sculpted EVA midsole. A translucent support tube takes inspiration from the older shoe’s nylon lace loops. 3M reflective detailing traces the wavy lines of the eyestay and midfoot overlay, providing added visibility in low-light conditions.

results.name: adidas Superstar Core Black Cloud White Gold
results.story: In honor of its 50th anniversary, the Superstar ‘Core Black White’ treats the iconic adidas low-top to an essential color scheme. The instantly recognizable rubber shell toe is finished in black, as are the sneaker’s full-grain leather upper and lightly textured midsole. Contrasting pops of white appear on the serrated leather three-stripes and heel tab. The latter element is stamped with a metallic gold Trefoil, matching additional branding hits atop the tongue and quarter panel.
